{"timestamp":"2026-05-25T17:45:07.020310Z","level":"info","event":"Done. Returned value was: [{'q': 'Everything is in your own heart.', 'a': 'Thich Nhat Hanh', 'c': 32, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Everything is in your own heart.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Thich Nhat Hanh</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Genius is the ability to act rightly without precedent - the power to do the right thing the first time.', 'a': 'Elbert Hubbard', 'c': 104, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Genius is the ability to act rightly without precedent - the power to do the right thing the first time.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Elbert Hubbard</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Everything that is done in the world is done by hope.', 'a': 'Martin Luther', 'c': 53, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Everything that is done in the world is done by hope.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Martin Luther</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"You don't know who is important to you until you actually lose them.\", 'a': 'Mahatma Gandhi', 'c': 68, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;You don&#039;t know who is important to you until you actually lose them.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Mahatma Gandhi</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'We must not cease from exploration. And the end of all our exploring will be to arrive where we began and to know the place for the first time.', 'a': 'T.S. Eliot', 'c': 143, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;We must not cease from exploration. And the end of all our exploring will be to arrive where we began and to know the place for the first time.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>T.S. Eliot</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Your visions will become clear only when you can look into your own heart. Who looks outside, dreams; who looks inside, awakes.', 'a': 'Carl Jung', 'c': 127, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Your visions will become clear only when you can look into your own heart. Who looks outside, dreams; who looks inside, awakes.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Carl Jung</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Where you are right now doesn't have to determine where you'll end up.\", 'a': 'Barack Obama', 'c': 70, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Where you are right now doesn&#039;t have to determine where you&#039;ll end up.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Barack Obama</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'We are shaped and fashioned by what we love.', 'a': 'Johann Wolfgang von Goethe', 'c': 44, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;We are shaped and fashioned by what we love.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Johann Wolfgang von Goethe</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'You gain strength, courage and confidence by every experience in which you really stop to look fear in the face.', 'a': 'Eleanor Roosevelt', 'c': 112, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;You gain strength, courage and confidence by every experience in which you really stop to look fear in the face.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Eleanor Roosevelt</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The path is difficult to ensure worthiness. The lazy look elsewhere, The persevering find riches.', 'a': 'Ming-Dao Deng', 'c': 97, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The path is difficult to ensure worthiness. The lazy look elsewhere, The persevering find riches.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Ming-Dao Deng</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Remember that this moment is not your life, it's just a moment in your life. Focus on what is in front of you, right now.\", 'a': 'Ryan Holiday', 'c': 121, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Remember that this moment is not your life, it&#039;s just a moment in your life. Focus on what is in front of you, right now.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Ryan Holiday</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"If you can't fly, run. If you can't run, walk. If you can't walk, crawl, but by all means, keep moving.\", 'a': 'Martin Luther King, Jr.', 'c': 103, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;If you can&#039;t fly, run. If you can&#039;t run, walk. If you can&#039;t walk, crawl, but by all means, keep moving.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Martin Luther King, Jr.</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Do not go where the path may lead, go instead where there is no path and leave a trail.', 'a': 'Ralph Waldo Emerson', 'c': 87, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Do not go where the path may lead, go instead where there is no path and leave a trail.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Ralph Waldo Emerson</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'If you only knew the magnificence of the 3, 6, and 9, then you would have a key to the universe.', 'a': 'Nikola Tesla', 'c': 96, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;If you only knew the magnificence of the 3, 6, and 9, then you would have a key to the universe.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Nikola Tesla</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'There are no uninteresting things, only uninterested people.', 'a': 'Gilbert Chesterton', 'c': 60, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;There are no uninteresting things, only uninterested people.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Gilbert Chesterton</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'You know you are on the road to success if you would do your job and not be paid for it.', 'a': 'Oprah Winfrey', 'c': 88, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;You know you are on the road to success if you would do your job and not be paid for it.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Oprah Winfrey</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'If you want the best the world has to offer, offer the world your best.', 'a': 'Neale Donald Walsch', 'c': 71, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;If you want the best the world has to offer, offer the world your best.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Neale Donald Walsch</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'You know the more one does the more one can do.', 'a': 'Amelia Earhart', 'c': 47, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;You know the more one does the more one can do.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Amelia Earhart</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Life without love is like a tree without blossoms or fruit.', 'a': 'Kahlil Gibran', 'c': 59, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Life without love is like a tree without blossoms or fruit.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Kahlil Gibran</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The road to success is always under construction..', 'a': 'Lily Tomlin', 'c': 50, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The road to success is always under construction..&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Lily Tomlin</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"If you don't like something change it; if you can't change it, change the way you think about it.\", 'a': 'Mary Engelbreit', 'c': 97, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;If you don&#039;t like something change it; if you can&#039;t change it, change the way you think about it.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Mary Engelbreit</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Inspire yourself to be great. Being good isn't good enough.\", 'a': 'Gurbaksh Chahal', 'c': 59, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Inspire yourself to be great. Being good isn&#039;t good enough.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Gurbaksh Chahal</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The measure of wisdom is how calm you are when facing any given situation.', 'a': 'Naval Ravikant', 'c': 74, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The measure of wisdom is how calm you are when facing any given situation.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Naval Ravikant</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"What we know is a drop, what we don't know is an ocean.\", 'a': 'Isaac Newton', 'c': 55, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;What we know is a drop, what we don&#039;t know is an ocean.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Isaac Newton</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The purpose of life is to live it, to taste experience to the utmost, to reach out eagerly and without fear for newer and richer experience.', 'a': 'Eleanor Roosevelt', 'c': 140, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The purpose of life is to live it, to taste experience to the utmost, to reach out eagerly and without fear for newer and richer experience.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Eleanor Roosevelt</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"If they wrote it to make money, don't read it.\", 'a': 'Naval Ravikant', 'c': 46, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;If they wrote it to make money, don&#039;t read it.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Naval Ravikant</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Life goes by fast. Enjoy it. Calm down. It's all funny.\", 'a': 'Joan Rivers', 'c': 55, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Life goes by fast. Enjoy it. Calm down. It&#039;s all funny.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Joan Rivers</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'He who has overcome his fears will truly be free.', 'a': 'Aristotle', 'c': 49, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;He who has overcome his fears will truly be free.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Aristotle</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Never regret your past. Rather, embrace it as the teacher that it is.', 'a': 'Robin Sharma', 'c': 69, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Never regret your past. Rather, embrace it as the teacher that it is.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Robin Sharma</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Unless someone truly has the power to say no, they never truly have the power to say yes.', 'a': 'Dan Millman', 'c': 89, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Unless someone truly has the power to say no, they never truly have the power to say yes.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Dan Millman</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'I am not what happened to me, I am what I choose to become.', 'a': 'Carl Jung', 'c': 59, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;I am not what happened to me, I am what I choose to become.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Carl Jung</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'No man is happy who does not think himself so.', 'a': 'Norman Vincent Peale', 'c': 46, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;No man is happy who does not think himself so.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Norman Vincent Peale</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Each day provides it's own gifts.\", 'a': 'Marcus Aurelius', 'c': 33, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Each day provides it&#039;s own gifts.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Marcus Aurelius</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Change is inevitable but personal growth is a choice.', 'a': 'Bob Proctor', 'c': 53, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Change is inevitable but personal growth is a choice.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Bob Proctor</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The destiny of man is in his own soul.', 'a': 'Herodotus', 'c': 38, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The destiny of man is in his own soul.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Herodotus</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'For the things we have to learn before we can do them, we learn by doing them.', 'a': 'Aristotle', 'c': 78, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;For the things we have to learn before we can do them, we learn by doing them.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Aristotle</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Don't wish it were easier, wish you were better.\", 'a': 'Jim Rohn', 'c': 48, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Don&#039;t wish it were easier, wish you were better.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Jim Rohn</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Sometimes a change of perspective is all it takes to see the light.', 'a': 'Dan Brown', 'c': 67, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Sometimes a change of perspective is all it takes to see the light.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Dan Brown</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'If I persist long enough I will win.', 'a': 'Og Mandino', 'c': 36, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;If I persist long enough I will win.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Og Mandino</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Winners are not afraid of losing. But losers are. Failure is part of the process of success. People who avoid failure also avoid success.', 'a': 'Robert Kiyosaki', 'c': 137, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Winners are not afraid of losing. But losers are. Failure is part of the process of success. People who avoid failure also avoid success.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Robert Kiyosaki</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Some people don't like change, but you need to embrace change if the alternative is disaster.\", 'a': 'Elon Musk', 'c': 93, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Some people don&#039;t like change, but you need to embrace change if the alternative is disaster.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Elon Musk</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'There is peace even in the storm.', 'a': 'Vincent van Gogh', 'c': 33, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;There is peace even in the storm.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Vincent van Gogh</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Realize deeply that the present moment is all you ever have.', 'a': 'Eckhart Tolle', 'c': 60, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Realize deeply that the present moment is all you ever have.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Eckhart Tolle</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'People are weird. When we find someone with weirdness that is compatible with ours, we team up and call it love.', 'a': 'Dr. Seuss', 'c': 112, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;People are weird. When we find someone with weirdness that is compatible with ours, we team up and call it love.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Dr. Seuss</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'A dream you dream alone is only a dream. A dream you dream together is reality.', 'a': 'Yoko Ono', 'c': 79, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;A dream you dream alone is only a dream. A dream you dream together is reality.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Yoko Ono</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'A wise man makes his own decisions, but an ignorant man mindlessly follows the crowd.', 'a': 'Chinese Proverb', 'c': 85, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;A wise man makes his own decisions, but an ignorant man mindlessly follows the crowd.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Chinese Proverb</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Adults are just children who earn money.', 'a': 'Kenneth Branagh', 'c': 40, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Adults are just children who earn money.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Kenneth Branagh</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Success is not final, failure is not fatal: it is the courage to continue that counts.', 'a': 'Winston Churchill', 'c': 86, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Success is not final, failure is not fatal: it is the courage to continue that counts.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Winston Churchill</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'You must find the place inside yourself where nothing is impossible.', 'a': 'Les Brown', 'c': 68, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;You must find the place inside yourself where nothing is impossible.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Les Brown</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'I admire those who do good and expect nothing in return.', 'a': 'Roy T. Bennett', 'c': 56, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;I admire those who do good and expect nothing in return.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Roy T. Bennett</footer></blockquote>'}]","logger":"airflow.task.operators.airflow.sdk.definitions.asset.decorators._AssetMainOperator","filename":"python.py","lineno":229}
